description: This file should contain a Solana wallet private key. For security reasons, the actual private key has been removed.
instructions: To use this project, create a Solana wallet using 'solana-keygen new --outfile wallet.json' and fund it with SOL before deploying tokens.
warning: NEVER commit actual wallet private keys to git repositories. This could result in loss of funds.
format: This file should contain an array of integers representing the wallet's private key bytes.
